<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4578174>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 9. — Chlidonophora chuni Blochmann,1900,Mozambique Channel,Bazaruto transect,MAINBAZA:A, B, dorsal view of complete specimen (MNHN IB-2013- 55), and enlargement of the umbonal part (B) to show details of the beak, stn CC 3158, 1220-1248 m; C, D, inner view of dorsal valve (MNHN IB-2013-56) with preserved subplectolophous lophophore, (D) enlargement of lophophore, stn CC 3157, 1410-1416 m; E, F, inner view of ventral valve (MNHN IB-2013-57) and enlargement of umbonal part (F), stn CC 3157; G-J, inner and oblique views of dorsal valve (MNHN IB-2013-58), enlargement (I) and tilted view (J) of posterior part to show cardinalia and loop, stn CC 3157; K, L, inner and tilted views of posterior part of dorsal valve (MNHN IB-2013-59), stn CC 3157. All SEMs. Scale bars: A, C, E, G, H, 2 mm; B, F, D, I-L, 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4578174/files/figure.png" .

